title: Jindal's latest book released as his 2016 campaign struggles
text: BATON ROUGE, La. (AP) - Republican presidential contender Bobby Jindal offers history from a conservative viewpoint in a new book illustrating the " folly of looking to the government for the solution to all of our problems.
